
 

B.PROJECT REPORT :–
For this task, I made a digital literacy awareness infographic using Canva. I chose Canva because it is very easy to use and has many good templates, which made my work simpler. In my infographic, I included topics like what digital literacy means, some useful tools for students, safe internet practices, and how to maintain a good online presence.
While making it, I tried to keep everything simple and easy to understand. I used short points and icons so that anyone can quickly read and understand the information without getting confused. My main goal was to create something helpful for my classmates so they can learn how to use digital platforms in a safe and smart way.
At first, I found it a bit difficult to adjust all the information in one page because it started looking crowded. But after trying a few designs, I managed to organize it properly. This task was interesting for me because I got to learn how to present information in a better and more creative way




